antMorrisonsBatman" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/GrantMorrisonsBatman">Grant Morrison's Batman</a> | <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/Nightwing" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/Nightwing">Nightwing</a></em> | <em>The Psyba-Rats</em> | <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/Superboy" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/Superboy">Superboy</a>/<a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/RobinSeries" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/RobinSeries">Robin</a>: World's Finest Three</em> | <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/ActionComics" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/ActionComics">Action Comics</a></em> <sup>(guest)</sup> | <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/Anarky" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/Anarky">Anarky</a></em> <sup>(guest)</sup> | <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/BlueBeetle" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/BlueBeetle">Blue Beetle</a></em> | <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/GothamCitySirens" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/GothamCitySirens">Gotham City Sirens</a></em> | <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/Impulse" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/Impulse">Impulse</a></em> | <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/BatmanAndTheOutsiders" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/BatmanAndTheOutsiders">The Outsiders</a></em> <sup>(guest)</sup> | <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/ResurrectionMan" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/ResurrectionMan">Resurrection Man</a></em> <sup>(guest)</sup> | <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/SevenSoldiers" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/SevenSoldiers">Seven Soldiers of Victory</a></em> | <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/Shadowpact" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/Shadowpact">Shadowpact</a></em> <sup>(guest)</sup> |